@author Daniel Csillag (aka. dccsillag)
@what My packages to autoinstall on a new computer.

Explanation:
~tag: tag this packages as
~what: a name for the package that is not distro-specific

~no: this package is unavailable in this distro/package manager
~skip: this package is unecessary in this distro/package manager - skip.

~tag        ~what                         Ubuntu                 ManjaroLinux                      conda-forge
